title: America Again: Re-becoming the Greatness We Never Weren't
description:
America Again: Re-becoming the Greatness We Never Weren't
by Stephen Colbert
Audiobook

runtime: 3 hours, 12 minutes, 13 seconds
bitrate: 64kbit/s (don't worry, it sounds fine.  64kbit sounds low for music, but it is normal for spoken word)

I can't believe no one has submitted this yet!  This is the one that Stephen Colbert  won the 2014 Grammy Award for Best Spoken Word Album.

From the wiki: "Colbert addresses topics including Wall Street, campaign finance, energy policy, eating on the campaign trail, and the United States Constitution."

It's a hilarious audiobook.  Enjoy!
